All Implemented Interfaces:
BusinessObjectModule, ReadAndUpsertBOM
public class SectionConfigReadAndUpsertBOMImpl
extends AppResourceReadAndUpsertBOMImpl

This is the ReadAndUpsert Business Object Module implementation for a Section Configuration BOM. A Section Configuration BOM consists of the .sec file and its associated .properties file. Both are stored on the database in the AppResource table. This class is responsible for updating or inserting a section onto the target system.

convertBusinessObjectContentToXML

public org.w3c.dom.Document convertBusinessObjectContentToXML(BusinessObjectIdentifier boIdentifier)
                                                       throws AppException,
                                                              InformationalException
This method takes in a section ID as the key for the Section BOM, and uses this key to retrieve the appResource record for the XML file and the associated .properties file for the Section BOM. All of this information is then stored in XML format as specified by the BOM infrastructure.
